What you need to know:

The legislators, who did not want to go on record, accused Ms Kassait of being IEBC’s face of impunity.Ms Kassait was a key player in the disputed 2017 polls.President Uhuru Kenyatta nominated Ms Kassait in a message that was read out to the House on Tuesday.If appointed, Ms Kassait will be tasked to seal loopholes in personal data breaches to curb cyber insecurity. 